{"tid":385681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭東鐵 撞左幾件蝻 蝗 同廢老出車門","createTime":"2017-09-03T11:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T16:13:43.000Z","uid":11779,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82da6e95d731b70b010d1bf44f1f514080bc13eb","tid":385681,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"係紅磡站時，我未落車 成班蝻 蝗同廢老就爭住衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知衝入黎做乜柒 明明大把位坐. 我就側一側身 雙手插袋（廢時比班呀嬋屈非禮）一野頂左三件出車門 （一個蝻 一個水貨蝗同一件廢老）我望住佢地深深不忿但又唔敢出聲個衰樣就好笑.<br />\n<br />\n所以手足有時間就做下gym啦 同埋記有leg day，到時個個300斯巴達人咁彈就有本錢講港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d20bd0dc29260efb449d81b4880233acef69be","tid":385681,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"9e4d19ad8fa31a9e3b4229d11ef3c71c66da8609","tid":385681,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f36d793785189a10ab48cd0c2ccbf82faad3b1","tid":385681,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9834cee7e39e47396cf14c6802ed9646ff2b7323","tid":385681,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9bc97fad7122e119b2baec13cc0e6d5fd1d7b31","tid":385681,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"ching好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94ac78321f328adb038f1a237fd32d7ceade9cd","tid":385681,"uid":73455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"上次畀個廢老撞完望咗佢一眼都畀佢鬧到狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ching好波呀！"},{"pid":"19cad1b1e4806